OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCouncil tax could rise by  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F#220, say researchers      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Council tax in England could rise by as
OL,6, much as #220 per year within three     
OL,7, years, researchers have said.          
OL,9,FThis is to keep local services running 
OL,10,Fand help pay for social care reforms,  
OL,11,Fthe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS) 
OL,12,Fthink tank said.                       
OL,14,FIt comes amid warnings that councils   
OL,15,Fcontinue to face severe funding        
OL,16,Fpressures due to the pandemic and must 
OL,17,Ffind new sources of income.            
OL,19,FThe government said it had given them  
OL,20,F#12bn since the start of the crisis.   
